3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - Although not directly related to social networks, the paper deals with the processing and analysis of SAR images, which can be considered as a form of network data. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image processing and enhancement, which is a core area of multimedia research. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Although not explicitly mentioned, the paper may involve machine learning techniques for image analysis and processing.
